892
00:58:41,963 --> 00:58:42,964
Jika Anda tahu,

893
00:58:43,048 --> 00:58:46,801
Anda tak akan susun skenario
di mana korban suntik diri sendiri.

894
00:58:46,885 --> 00:58:48,678
